Now available, shop the collection on oscardelarenta.com.

The #MyODLRAlibi challenge has returned for the holidays! Oscar de la Renta, house-friend @tinaleung and our socially-distant studio audience invite you to design your very own Alibi bag with a seasonal twist. 

Doodle, adorn, and/or make a 3-D masterpiece and share your interpretation with us. The creator, hand-selected by Co-Creative Directors Fernando Garcia and Laura Kim, will win an Oscar de la Renta Alibi bag. ⁣
⁣
How to Participate: ⁣
⁣
Download the folding pattern from the link in our bio, print it, add your creative touch and assemble!⁣
⁣
Upload an image or video on Instagram of your assembled bag with the hashtag #MyODLRAlibi and #odlrholiday to win.
⁣
This contest runs until Saturday, December 26th 10AM EST

Show us your Alibi. Oscar de la Renta and design team member, David Alperti (@princemonkey), invite you to design your very own Alibi bag. Inspired by vintage luggage, the house-favorite Alibi combines old-world and contemporary appeal. ⁣
⁣
Doodle, adorn, and/or make a 3-D masterpiece and share your interpretation with us. The top three creators, hand-selected by co-creative directors Fernando Garcia and Laura Kim, will win an Oscar de la Renta Alibi. ⁣
⁣
How to Participate: ⁣
⁣
Download the folding pattern from the link in our bio, print it, add your creative touch and assemble!⁣
⁣
Upload an image or digital file on Instagram of your assembled bag with the hashtag #MyODLRAlibi to win.
⁣
This contest runs until Friday, May 22nd 10 AM EST

node.text: From castings to the runway, face time with the girls of #odlrfall2020. Video by @carlospierucci.

Taking inspiration from Wolfgang von Goethe’s 1797 poem ‘The Sorcerer’s Apprentice’ and storied New York City nightlife, Fall 2020 captures the enchantment of a magical evening. The historic stage for the show was The New York Public Library - Stephen A. Schwarzman Building, where models took to the runway and its iconic steps in sleek daywear and exquisite evening in color-bright hues. Video by @indigitalimages.
